Exposure is handcrafted and the current setting is 0.2, which is a good value in the outdoor environment. 

Gain value of the left camera is set to "AUTO", which means the camera driver will automatically tune the gain value to adapt to the environment. 

To make the left and right images have the same brightness. The gain value of the left camera is set to follow the gain value of the right camera.

All the other settings can be found in the Algorithm Design Documentation (ADD).
  
